videos.headline: Bird finds Stewart for transition jumper
videos.description: Sue Bird comes up with the rebound and pushes the pace to find Breanna Stewart who nails the mid-range jumper.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Bird finds Stewart for transition jumper) 2020/10/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCoughtry swishes wide-open 3
videos.description: Seattles' defense leaves Angel McCoughtry wide open and she makes them pay with a 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Stewart's 3 has Storm bench on their feet
videos.description: Breanna Stewart pulls up for a 3 in transition to the delight of her teammates.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Stewart's 3 has Storm bench on their feet) 2020/10/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bird breaks WNBA Finals single-game assists record in 3rd quarter
videos.description: Sue Bird sets up a Breanna Stewart jumper for her 12th assist of the night, a WNBA Finals record.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Bird breaks WNBA Finals single-game assists record in 3rd quarter) 2020/10/2 ESHEET
